{"tid":983304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡雲尼暗示下年退役","createTime":"2019-01-16T00:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T06:18:43.000Z","uid":199590,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d8a7100e567de40e802a9e24505b2218c7e4ea99","tid":983304,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T00:14:57.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=e6KkJSHDiHBqtimTWL5KH10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=66312426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】射手卡雲尼下月將滿32歲，他透露跟巴黎聖日耳門的合約於2020年完結時，或會就此掛靴。<br />\n<br />\n雖然卡雲尼（Edinson Cavani）年紀不輕，但近年仍入球如麻，在2016/17球季在36場法甲轟入35球，上季亦於32場聯賽攻下28個入球，以157球超越伊巴謙莫域，成為巴黎聖日耳門史上入球王。<br />\n<br />\n近年皆有傳卡雲尼會離隊，當中拿玻里就極力爭取把他帶回「家」，但這名烏拉圭國腳表示：「我希望留下來，直至合約完結，或許那就是我球員生涯的終點。我不知道自己在2020年後，會否繼續踢球，或者會否留在巴黎。」<br />\n<br />\n自尼馬加盟後，經常傳出跟卡雲尼不和，兩人更曾在場上爆發爭射12碼風波，但卡雲尼坦言在PSG過得十分愉快，掛靴的想法並非因為不如意：「我在巴黎感覺很好，球會也很滿意我，我希望在這裡完成合約。」"},{"pid":"5b501791a6f3a7db2c49c8fa77c88688ab8f27d3","tid":983304,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T00:20:41.000Z","msg":"唔係話返烏拉圭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c613d9c97b1ae73a9faef4aa02caf58a3be9877b","tid":983304,"uid":24121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T00:21:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e00ca857bf672c5352b8014b075735f824916659","tid":983304,"uid":86316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MDrrdPOwSf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMDrrdPOwSf4&d=e6KkJSHDiHBqtimTWL5KH10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=31690cec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MDrrdPOwSf4</a>"},{"pid":"5b1a1a53ec8250270dfbe5503bb5dcdbb7507d79","tid":983304,"uid":226925,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:03:58.000Z","msg":"32歲就退<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1126b03e214de18df797589d27c476d630305d7a","tid":983304,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T02:17:20.000Z","msg":"急流勇退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ed1974c1f2109f6fcca28585218812edbef42d","tid":983304,"uid":17387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:31:52.000Z","msg":"退你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cad226ada2788435ac7fb80bf64c4d11197a937","tid":983304,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:32:47.000Z","msg":"唔會咁早掛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d2c239eb054b1ee2dd0780efc7868e3e8442d9","tid":983304,"uid":63253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"「我希望留下來，直至合約完結，或許那就是我球員生涯的終點。我不知道自己在2020年後，會否繼續踢球，或者會否留在巴黎。」<br />\n<br />\n標題想點？"},{"pid":"1d73879d93727eaa56c18baac36f556d4c38ff5d","tid":983304,"uid":91546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"最少踢到35啦"},{"pid":"b5e1a20ae0185010af0da802ee9a20db52cb5bb6","tid":983304,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e00ca857bf672c5352b8014b075735f824916659","tid":983304,"uid":86316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T00:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MDrrdPOwSf4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMDrrdPOwSf4&d=e6KkJSHDiHBqtimTWL5KH10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=31690cec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MDrrdPOwSf4</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T03:49:13.000Z","msg":"卡雲尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e7f4194739562d8a6358b4da670d0a